channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Kamala Says Being a 'Leader Is Based on Who You Lift Up'—Then Immediately Appears to Call Trump 'Coward'
Biden committed ‘impeachable conduct,’ ‘defrauded United States to enrich his family’: House GOP report
item.description: President Biden engaged in “impeachable conduct," “abused his office" and “defrauded the United States to enrich his family," House Republicans allege in highly anticipated report.

item.title: Michelle Obama to Address DNC on Tuesday
item.description: Michelle Obama will address the Democratic National Convention on Tuesday, USA Today reported.

item.title: Kamala's Gobbledygook Answer About Paying for Her Spending Shows Exactly Why They Don't Let Her Talk
Catholic Charities asks Supreme Court to protect First Amendment rights in battle against the state
item.description: A Catholic Charities group in Wisconsin is appealing to the U.S. Supreme Court in its fight to stay exempt from the state's unemployment program.

item.title: Harris Arrives in Chicago to Star at Democratic Convention
item.description: Kamala Harris arrived in Chicago on Sunday ahead of her star turn at the Democratic National Convention, perhaps the most pivotal moment yet for her short but stunning election campaign against Donald Trump.

item.title: DNC Premiering Their 'Molech Mobile' Shows How Much They Hate Life and Despise Black Voters
DNC kicks off in Chicago to nominate Harris-Walz as anti-Israel protesters prepare counter-rally
item.description: The Democratic National Convention begins Monday, as top Democrats travel to Chicago to celebrate the nomination of Vice President Kamala Harris as the party’s presidential nominee.

item.title: Harris Implies Trump a 'Coward' During Pa. Campaign Stop
item.description: Vice President Kamala Harris indirectly criticized former President Donald Trump on Sunday, suggesting her opponent in the Nov. 5 election was a "coward" whose politics focused on putting down rivals.

item.title: Biden's Former Chief of Staff Admits Kamala Harris Vice Presidency Was a Failure
Flashback: Obama was one of earliest big-name Dems to endorse Walz at dawn of his political career
item.description: Former President Obama was one of the few high-profile Democrats to campaign for Tim Walz during his first congressional run in 2006, the Minnesota governor said in 2017.

item.title: House Intel's Turner: Let Ukraine Have Long-Range Weapons Systems
item.description: Restrictions placed on Kyiv by the Biden administration in its war with Russia are counterproductive, Rep. Mike Turner told CBS News' "Face the Nation" on Sunday, stating that Ukraine having long-range weapon systems could change the dynamics on the ground.

item.title: Kamala Has Another Embarrassing Failure As Talking Points Take a Hit During Remarks in NC
Dems project images on Trump Tower ahead of DNC
item.description: The Democratic National Committee will project images directly onto Trump International Hotel and Tower in Chicago on Sunday as the party gets ready to start its convention.

item.title: Rep. Turner Slams Biden for 'Not Holding Iran Accountable'
item.description: The Biden administration is "not holding Iran accountable" after American officials warned earlier this month that Tehran was attempting to influence the U.S. election, House Intelligence Committee Chair Rep. Mike Turner told CBS News' "Face the Nation" on Sunday.
